</div>
<div class="col-lg-4">
<p>My name is Debashis Barman and I am a Freelance front end Web Designer. I try to make the websites I design and build as simple and intuitive to use as possible whilst still having a unique aesthetic appeal. I specialise in responsive front-end design, HTML/CSS and web typography.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-4">
<p>When I'm free, I spend my time exploring places and beyond, adventuring in the wilderness, working on tiny side projects, writing, romancing my <em>lovely girlfriend</em>, sketching and doodling, <span class="fun">reading</span> short stories and novels, listening to music and playing games. And internet. I love internet.</p>
</div>
</div>
